com.viaoa.util

Class OAXMLReader1

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
      • com.viaoa.util.OAXMLReader1
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.xml.sax.ContentHandler, org.xml.sax.DTDHandler, org.xml.sax.EntityResolver, org.xml.sax.ErrorHandler

    public class OAXMLReader1
extends org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
    OAXMLReader using a SAXParser to parse and automatically create OAObjects from a XML file. This will do the following to find the existing object: 1: if OAProperty.importMatch, then it will search to find a matching object 2: if objectId props, then it will search to find a matching object 3: use guid if not found, then a new object will be created.
    See Also:
    OAXMLWriter
